OL,3,CChildren's Hospice position over
OL,4,Ccutting beds 'unchanged'
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Children's
OL,7,FHospice has said its position over
OL,8,Freducing some services remains
OL,9,Funchanged despite an intervention from
OL,10,Fthe Stormont Health Minister.JLast
OL,11,Fweek the hospice said it was
OL,12,Fconsidering cutting bed places due to
OL,13,Fa bleak financial outlook.JIt cited a
OL,14,Floss of state funding and other
OL,15,Fchallenges presented by the cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving crisis.JThe hospice, which is
OL,17,Flocated in north Belfast, provides
OL,18,Fspecialist palliative care for more
OL,19,Fthan 350 babies, children and their
OL,20,Ffamilies every year.
